rical building admiring the details of the architecture before taking a look inside. The interior, although simple, is beautiful. It&#x2019;s worth visiting for the upper level, where you can see amazing views out over the rest of Pisa.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Entry fee:<\/strong> &#x20AC;7 EUR<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143708\/SA72616.jpg\" alt=\"pisa italy Piazza dei Miracoli \"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"pisa italy Piazza dei Miracoli \" class=\"wp-image-68836 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143708\/SA72616.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143708\/SA72616-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143708\/SA72616-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143708\/SA72616-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143708\/SA72616-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143708\/SA72616-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143708\/SA72616-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/