--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/florence\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Best things to do in Florence, Italy<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/66498&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14114938\/Things-to-do-Pisa-Italy-1.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14114938\/Things-to-do-Pisa-Italy-1-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14114938\/Things-to-do-Pisa-Italy-1-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"11 Best Things To Do in Pisa, Italy\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-cattedrale-de-pisa\">Cattedrale de Pisa<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Cathedral of Pisa (Santa Maria Assunta) is often forgotten about in favor of the Leaning Tower of Pisa. However, it stands right next door and is a historical gem in its own right. The beautiful Romanesque building is made from white marble that&#x2019;s been intricately carved and sculpted. Inside, you can find more marble, as well as religious relics, gold gilding, and beautiful paintings.&#xA0;&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Make sure to see the famous pulpit carved from marble by the renowned sculptor Giovanni Pisano.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14110833\/pisa16.jpg\" alt=\"Cattedrale de Pisa italy\"><\/noscript><img width=\"251\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Cattedrale de Pisa italy\" class=\"wp-image-68893 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1427px) 100vw, 1427px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14110833\/pisa16.jpg 1427w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14110833\/pisa16-446x600.jpg 446w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content