4.jpg 1281w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14110240\/pisa-24-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14110240\/pisa-24-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-piazza-dei-miracoli-square-of-miracles\">Piazza dei Miracoli (Square of Miracles)<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The leaning tower of Pisa, Cathedral, Camposanto, and Baptisterium all sit in a beautiful grass square that&#x2019;s free of cars. This area is now a designated <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/travel-blog\/best-unesco-world-heritage-sites\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">UNESCO<\/a> world heritage site because of its cultural and historical significance. After you&#x2019;ve visited all the sights, spend a few hours just lying in the grass around the monuments. This is a beautiful way to spend an afternoon in Pisa!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read<\/strong>: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/travel-blog\/best-unesco-world-heritage-sites\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Must-see UNESCO world heritage sites<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14110230\/pisa-23.jpg\" alt=\"pisa Piazza dei Miracoli\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"333\" alt=\"pisa Piazza dei Miracoli\" class=\"wp-image-68887 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14110230\/pisa-23.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14110230\/pisa-23-800x592.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14110230\/pisa-23-1080x799.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14110230\/pisa-23-450x333.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14110230\/pisa-23-30x22.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14110230\/pisa-23-163x121.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14110230\/pisa-23-243x180.jpg 243w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14110230\/pisa-23-768x568.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14110230\/pisa-23-1024x757.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14110230\/pisa-23-1440x1065.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14110230\/pisa-23-300x222.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14110230\/pisa-23-600x444.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14110230\/pisa-23-30x22.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14110230\/pisa-23.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-santa-maria-della-spina\">Santa Maria Della Spina<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Pisa has lots of churches, but Santa Maria Della Spina is arguably the most beautiful of them all. This tiny church has a detailed gothic facade and has a unique setting on the riverbank. Della Spina means &#x2018;of the thorn&#x2019; as one of the thorns from Jesus&#x2019; thorn crown once rested at this site.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Entry fee<\/strong>: &#x20AC;1.50 EUR<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143719\/SA72633.jpg\" alt=\"pisa italy city guide\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"pisa italy city guide\" class=\"wp-image-68838 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143719\/SA72633.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143719\/SA72633-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143719\/SA72633-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143719\/SA72633-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143719\/SA72633-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143719\/SA72633-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143719\/SA72633-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143719\/SA72633-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143719\/SA72633-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143719\/SA72633-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143719\/SA72633-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143719\/SA72633-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143719\/SA72633-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143719\/SA72633-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143719\/SA72633.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-gelateria-de-coltelli\">Gelateria De&#x2019; Coltelli<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Gelato is life in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Italy<\/a> and Pisa does it very well. There are plenty of places to grab some refreshing ice cream, but the most famous is the Gelateria De&#x2019; Coltelli. It&#x2019;s known for its exotic gelato flavors, where people can choose anything from candied lemon peel to ginger. Plus, it&#x2019;s got a great location on the banks of the River Arno.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/pisa-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Click here to see to hotels in Pisa<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-borgo-stretto\">Borgo Stretto<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Borgo Stretto is the most important shopping street in all of Pisa. However, it&#x2019;s not just for shopping; it&#x2019;s the perfect place to admire the beautiful <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Italian<\/a> townhouses painted in terracottas and pinks with their wooden shutters and hanging washing. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143729\/SA72673.jpg\" alt=\"best things to do pisa italy\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best things to do pisa italy\" class=\"wp-image-68840 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143729\/SA72673.jpg 1281w, https:\