pg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154756\/pisa-11-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154756\/pisa-11-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154756\/pisa-11-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154756\/pisa-11-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154756\/pisa-11-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154756\/pisa-11-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154756\/pisa-11-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154756\/pisa-11-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154756\/pisa-11-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154756\/pisa-11.jpg 1281w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154756\/pisa-11-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154756\/pisa-11-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-kieth-haring-house\">Kieth Haring House<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Kieth Haring is a famous artist known for his vibrant murals. He painted this huge mural across one side of a grand <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Italian<\/a> house with an array of colors. The abstract piece depicts moving people, meant to represent life and vitality. What&#x2019;s unusual about this piece is the unique mixture of old and new, with the modern work splashed across a traditional home wall. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Visiting the Keith Haring house is undoubtedly a special thing to do in Pisa!<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-palazzo-della-carovana\">Palazzo Della Carovana<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Palazzo Della Carovana is a stunning square that sits at the very center of Pisa, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Italy<\/a>. Known as the Knights Square, it&#x2019;s home to fascinating historical buildings such as the magnificent Palace of the Elders and the Normale di Pisa University. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143741\/SA72686.jpg\" alt=\"pisa italy Palazzo Della Carovana\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"pisa italy Palazzo Della Carovana\" class=\"wp-image-68842 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143741\/SA72686.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143741\/SA72686-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143741\/SA72686-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143741\/SA72686-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143741\/SA72686-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143741\/SA72686-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143741\/SA72686-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143741\/SA72686-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143741\/SA72686-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143741\/SA72686-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143741\/SA72686-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143741\/SA72686-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143741\/SA72686-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143741\/SA72686-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13143741\/SA72686.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The square is incredibly rich in history. In fact, the university was founded by Napoleon Bonaparte, and the library was once the seat of the government in the middle ages. Now, it&#x2019;s a great place to come and hang out, watching the students go about their day amongst the series of beautiful buildings. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sadly, most of these buildings aren&#x2019;t accessible for the public, but they&#x2019;re still worth a visit and one of the top things to do in Pisa.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n              