rhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-italy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your rental car here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<p>It&#x2019;s also got a beautiful train station where you can find trains leaving to other major cities in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Italy<\/a>, such as <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/rome\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Rome<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/florence\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Florence<\/a>, Naples, and Turin.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154808\/pisa-12.jpg\" alt=\"pisa things to do\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"pisa things to do\" class=\"wp-image-68854 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154808\/pisa-12.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154808\/pisa-12-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154808\/pisa-12-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154808\/pisa-12-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154808\/pisa-12-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154808\/pisa-12-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154808\/pisa-12-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154808\/pisa-12-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/13154808\/pisa-12-1024x683.jpg 1024w, 